Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly into the wavy and twisted sky,\Ninto your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance created between us\Nbecame too big,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because we were always together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your honest reply, “See you…”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.99,0:00:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,coming from that brash mouth\Nmakes it sadder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are in an unfamiliar town, crying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want to deliver you a smile,\Neven if I’m not by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly into the wavy and twisted sky,\Ninto your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it so close,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our two hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bewildering Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kids, get out of here\Nif you don’t wanna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better not think lightly of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not gonna hand this guy over,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Dropouts…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not gonna end up with\Nyou just getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re gonna get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Multi-Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Blood Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Todoroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Jutsu isn’t Ninjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Killer Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just barely.\NMore importantly, where’s Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everybody safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. However, Commander Todoroki\Nis nowhere to be seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Let go, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not getting back\Nwith your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Todoroki! Gantetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah… We’re fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve gotten separated from\NSakura and Bushy Brows…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn’t any question in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my mission to deliver\Nthis guy to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the ship’s been destroyed, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are pursuing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they’re gonna steal this guy\Naway from us anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be better to\Ntake care of him right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean take care of him…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we delivered him the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s certain that\Nhe’ll be sentenced to death…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than having them\Ntake him away, it would be better to…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not set in stone that\Nthey’ll be able to take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission is to guard this guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s exactly what my mission is too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you so much as try anything,\Nyour head’s gonna roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be fine…\Nnow that we’ve come this far…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we’ve totally lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve gone pretty deep\Ninto the forest, haven’t we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get our bearings from\Nthe position of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too dangerous to go back\Nto the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll continue straight through\Nthis forest to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it’s my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it’ll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said earlier you were going\Nto finish this guy off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about\Na worst-case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it…\NWell then, let’s get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sakura is all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Naruto…\NHe’s gonna be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let’s hurry up and link up with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detect something strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up above!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s follow him!\NThe enemy might have captured Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re walking in the direction\Nof the moon, right…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is the moon following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Forest of Bewilderment…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get lost you can\Nnever find you way out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He talked…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are in custody.\NYou’re not allowed to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Forest of Bewilderment…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know? Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninja Dropouts have\Na hide-out in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we were escorting you\Nthrough Ninja Dropout territory…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This forest is perfect for a hide-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fog, the winds that\Nsweep through the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the extreme magnetic fields…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all make a person lose\Ntheir sense of direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person finding himself in\Nthis forest for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will never find his way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t believe that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way we won’t find\Nour way out…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys won’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for me, a member of\Nthe Ninja Dropouts…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the outcome will be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will guide you through this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that’s right…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, a Ninja Dropout,\Nthis forest is like your backyard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let’s have you guide us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some kind of idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The finesse that the Ninja Dropouts\Nshowed earlier on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,makes sense if you think\Nthat this is their garden…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’ll believe you when you say\Nyou have a hide-out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:11:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then even more so…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more so, it's a no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is gonna pretend to\Nbe guiding us out of the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but will actually be taking us\Nto the hide-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Todoroki…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an emergency situation…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don’t kill him, we’ll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody’s gonna care…if this guy dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Todoroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took all the money the Ninja Dropouts\Nhad stolen up to now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was tortured…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys don’t want to rescue me…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just want to get that money\Nback from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they have the money back,\Nthose guys will kill me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think I’ll believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninja Dropouts hide-out is\Nhere in this forest, right…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it’s like\Na backyard to them too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like it is for Gantetsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since we've trespassed\Ninto their garden
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s likely that the Ninja Dropouts\Nwill come after us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether Gantetsu’s\Nbetrayed them or not…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think our only option is to\Npin our hopes on this guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure\Nyou know what you’re doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everything’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys won’t figure out\Nthis kind of circuitous route.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really trust this guy…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m used to it’s venom. It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really gonna be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it. You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Crimson Mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I combined the Shadow Clone Jutsu\Nand the Transformation Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it’s my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m gonna strike you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t think it’s gonna be that\Neasy to strike me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy! Trying to get away, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That sound is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you we made it…Gantetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to fight, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:20:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t… I won’t be fooled.\NYou…you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be safe if we just follow Gantetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Todoroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Todoroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were going to deliver\NGantetsu to the capital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way I’ll forgive this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy killed my family…\Nhe killed my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gantetsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Key to the rusted heart’s door
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will always be smiling right near by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if rains of spears were to fall,\NI will run through it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to find the joy\Nwithout a shape
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This big dream of mine that\Ncannot be translated to words,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make it come true,\Neven if it were to deepen my wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stand here today because of\Nwhat we believed through,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I will continue running forward,\Nnever looking away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I’m told that\Nthere is no bright future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll change it right away,\Nlighting it with all my feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is probably testing our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my heart, I gently grasped my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are probably searching for\Nthe answer to your tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream is always waiting near by,\Nwith the answers in its hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Key to the rusted heart’s door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will always be smiling right near by
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true that Gantetsu may be evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but how is taking revenge out\Non him going to change things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t our mission to take Gantetsu\Nto the capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I… I don’t think that\Nhe’s an evil person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you leave me\Nno choice if you won’t listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll stop you with all my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “Memory of Flames”
